HEADWORD: Famously
<hw>Fa"mous*ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a famous
manner; in a distinguished degree; greatly; splendidly.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Then this land was <qex>famously</qex> enriched⟦br⟧
